  "detailed_description": "A relaxing and wholesome \"clear-up\" cooking game. Match 3 objects to cook them in the pan. Don't let the pan get too full. Clear all the objects, clear your mind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809110/extras/2a63a2ca44d6519ab74f0660921ee156.poster.avif?t=1726497088\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809110/extras/2a63a2ca44d6519ab74f0660921ee156.webm?t=1726497088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809110/extras/2a63a2ca44d6519ab74f0660921ee156.mp4?t=1726497088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Match 3 objects to cook them in the pan<br></li><li>Don't let the pan get too full<br></li><li>Clear all the objects to pass the level<br></li><li>Perfect game for those that get satisfaction from clearing up clutter or hearing the sound of food sizzling. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809110/extras/0487335b35f139fee829f377275f999f.poster.avif?t=1726497088\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809110/extras/0487335b35f139fee829f377275f999f.webm?t=1726497088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809110/extras/0487335b35f139fee829f377275f999f.mp4?t=1726497088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Relaxing sounds that help you relax<br></li><li> If you like the sound of food sizzling, this game is perfect for you.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"http