/span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Just tap on an item<br></li><li> Simple satisfying gameplay</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Relaxing music and effects.<br></li><li> No timers, play at your own pace.<br></li><li> Over 200+ physics items.<br></li><li> Lots of unique level variations.<br></li><li> Quick levels. Levels range from 30 seconds up to 5 minutes.<br></li><li> Intuitive controls, just tap the item.<br></li><li> Helps you relax and de-stress.<br></li><li> Easy to pick up and play. Fun for all ages.<br></li><li> Various gameplay, graphics, and performance settings.</li></ul>",
